INSERT INTO msxdb_company VALUES ('629','Clover','','0','KR','Clover','An MSX copycat company similar to Zemina. Most of their games are unofficial ports. They also produced Joysticks and Famiclones, among other things.
INSERT INTO msxdb_company VALUES ('630','Aproman','','0','KR','','Originally a chain of home computer hardware/software stores, they also pushed forward development of original domestic games after the copyright law was enacted in Korea. They relied mostly on publishing software by external developers, it is not certain whether they had also an internal development team. They also used to distribute a bunch of language training programs, Hangeul word processors and Western edutainment titles. The last time they became involved with game publishing was upon the release of Mantra''s version of Ys 2. A PC systems retailer with the same name and logo registered in 2007. It doesn''t seem to be directly related, but rather just an hommage, though. 
